    "name": "Ghostly Condemnation",
    "prerequisite": "*Headless Haunt*",
    "subtype": "feat",
    "text": "You shriek a death sentence upon a single target within 120 feet, forcing it to experience the final moments of your mortal life as you were dragged through a howling mob and forced to kneel before the *final blade* that took your life and head. The target is subject to the effects of a 5th-rank *vision of death* with a DC equal to your class DC or spell DC, whichever is higher. If you slay a significant foe with this ability, its physical body is gruesomely decapitated, forcing its allies within 15 feet to attempt a Will save against the same DC or be frightened 1 (frightened 2 on a critical failure).",
